{"name":"Basic Magic","type":"power","img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/weapon_27.jpg","system":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":null},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Theurge"},"powerOriginName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Original Name","value":"Basic Magic"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"feature"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":""},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-c3dc270b-7fff-8a33-6913-297d1abff739\" dir=\"ltr\">Your main attacks are your magic basic attacks. These count as basic attacks for the purpose of things like making opportunity attacks (or a commander or bard&rsquo;s granting you extra basic attacks), and unlike a ranged spell you can use your magic ranged attack to target an enemy engaged with you without provoking an opportunity attack from it (exactly like any basic ranged attack). You still provoke from any other enemy engaged with you, however. In addition, you can&rsquo;t use your magic-based basic attacks while you are hampered.&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Your talents modify your magic basic attacks, and are designed so that you can apply multiple such talents to the same basic attack at once. You gain all of the talent&rsquo;s benefits for that attack, and penalties and bonuses to e.g. damage die size stack as you&rsquo;d expect. So an attack benefitting from both Mystical Might and Mass Enchantment would increase the damage die size by a single stage, for example.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"sustainOn":{"type":"Number","label":"Sustain On","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-1a805ca2-7fff-0c52-4e32-3e32c49e5fa4\">You can target far away enemies with your basic </span>magic ranged attack, at a -2 penalty to the attack roll.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}},"embeddedMacro":{"type":"String","label":"Embedded Macro","value":""}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.sTFAc3lJVuVupNRp.Item.VK3ufcd7gQ9s1fAY"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"archmage","systemVersion":"1.22.1","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666429682236,"modifiedTime":1666431888062,"lastModifiedBy":"Y7ZCCgrYWjKNyJtK"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Y7ZCCgrYWjKNyJtK":3},"_id":"16tNG7mYYZQKHrBa"}
{"name":"Protective Casting","type":"power","img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/weapon_27.jpg","system":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"once-per-battle"},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Theurge"},"powerOriginName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Original Name","value":"Protective Casting"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"interrupt"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-b785a5d6-7fff-d342-abbe-c113db021dcf\" dir=\"ltr\">Once per encounter, as an interrupt action you may add a +4 bonus to your own or an ally&rsquo;s AC. This is intended to let you negate a hit, and we assume the GM will let you know whether the bonus would actually help or not. If it doesn&rsquo;t, feel free to reuse this talent later in the battle (but you still burned your interrupt action this round, sorry).</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"sustainOn":{"type":"Number","label":"Sustain On","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-204ea2d9-7fff-0dc3-a033-d3a3b6960783\" dir=\"ltr\">The bonus applies to PD as well as AC.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-04ed1878-7fff-300f-690f-28ffa10f2f41\" dir=\"ltr\">You may use this talent twice per encounter.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-5dbca747-7fff-65d6-9084-cd584d3e2247\" dir=\"ltr\">The bonus applies to MD as well.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}},"embeddedMacro":{"type":"String","label":"Embedded Macro","value":""}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.sTFAc3lJVuVupNRp.Item.Jj7BcVxgMDbcq3Df"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"archmage","systemVersion":"1.22.1","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666431292740,"modifiedTime":1666431918090,"lastModifiedBy":"Y7ZCCgrYWjKNyJtK"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Y7ZCCgrYWjKNyJtK":3},"_id":"1QDpR7PKxm70Ccej"}
{"name":"War Caster","type":"power","img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/weapon_27.jpg","system":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":null},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Theurge"},"powerOriginName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Original Name","value":"War Caster"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":""},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-90b40f1e-7fff-b3b9-a12e-821f7a9fc177\" dir=\"ltr\">Reduce the penalty for using armor (not shields) by 2, and raise your AC in no armor to 13. Phrase this as actual armor or magical shields, as you prefer. In addition, your basic magic melee attack damage die size increases by two stages, usually from d4 to d8, and deals your level damage on a miss. Phrase it as short-range magic or a big flaming weapon or however you like and makes sense for your character. You can also cast any ranged spell you may have borrowed from other classes, or use your Conjurer talent if you have it, without triggering opportunity attacks. However, your basic magic attacks damage (not attack) bonus is now based on your Constitution, instead of your Intelligence, Wisdom or Charisma. You&rsquo;ll need the HP to survive in melee.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"sustainOn":{"type":"Number","label":"Sustain On","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e3f156ea-7fff-0b6d-e76b-794b1438a664\">Your recovery dice are now d8s instead of d6s.</span></p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-eb362251-7fff-3900-bd7a-aad9129c8c12\" dir=\"ltr\">Your base HP increases from 6 to 7.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-bc6d226a-7fff-548b-12e5-8d90340863a2\" dir=\"ltr\">Gain a +1 bonus to all defenses.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}},"embeddedMacro":{"type":"String","label":"Embedded Macro","value":""}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.sTFAc3lJVuVupNRp.Item.zvJUekJKmcK9Bqam"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"archmage","systemVersion":"1.22.1","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666431739429,"modifiedTime":1666431934879,"lastModifiedBy":"Y7ZCCgrYWjKNyJtK"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Y7ZCCgrYWjKNyJtK":3},"_id":"27rzC7LNe48fD2rF"}
{"name":"Wizardly Schooling","type":"power","img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/weapon_27.jpg","system":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":null},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Theurge"},"powerOriginName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Original Name","value":"Wizardly Schooling"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":""},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5f3b5261-7fff-6913-3721-a638db9d36ec\">You gain the Wizard&rsquo;s Cantrip class feature, and you can cast Utility Spell once per full heal-up at your level.</span></p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"sustainOn":{"type":"Number","label":"Sustain On","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-7b6153c1-7fff-a8ee-4974-2cc077625068\" dir=\"ltr\">You gain a single spell slot at your level that you can use to prepare a Wizard daily spell. You can change this spell during a full heal-up. Note that Wizard spells use Intelligence for their attack roll, so you may want to avoid this feat if you have low Intelligence, or at least focus on non-attack spells instead.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>You gain a 2nd Wizard spell slot, two levels lower than your level.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>You gain a 3rd Wizard spell slot, this one at your level.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}},"embeddedMacro":{"type":"String","label":"Embedded Macro","value":""}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.sTFAc3lJVuVupNRp.Item.6m3jOmFt2Th6H5qp"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"archmage","systemVersion":"1.22.1","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666431656979,"modifiedTime":1666431932248,"lastModifiedBy":"Y7ZCCgrYWjKNyJtK"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Y7ZCCgrYWjKNyJtK":3},"_id":"3DvfAl9ZvCWKdVEP"}
{"name":"Gemmartia","type":"power","img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/weapon_27.jpg","system":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"rechargeAttempts":{"type":"Number","label":"Number of Recharges Attempted","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Max Uses","value":1},"group":{"type":"String","label":"Group","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source Name","value":"Theurge"},"powerOriginName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Original Name","value":"Gemmartia"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"free"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e71f1549-7fff-e6f3-2eb0-ea026413e449\">A number of times per full heal-up equal to your Charisma modifier ([[@cha.mod]], minimum 1), you can as a free action add [[/r 1d4]] to one of your attack rolls. Yes, this is supposed to be used after you rolled, to hopefully let you turn that miss into a hit. You can only add one d4 per attack (so up to once per target, if you are using this in conjunction with </span>Mass Enchantment), and you can&rsquo;t use this on a nat. 1.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"sustainOn":{"type":"Number","label":"Sustain On","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2f862ee5-7fff-9bb5-ec7c-0d5c11786ac5\">If the attack still misses, deal half damage with it.</span></p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-193a85c8-7fff-bad3-2e00-fa580f18e8bf\">If the attack still misses, also regain the use of this talent you just spent.</span></p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-d303dbaa-7fff-de0f-9838-c21ff1c71fb1\">Increase the bonus to +[[/r 1d6]].</span></p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}},"embeddedMacro":{"type":"String","lab